text: Kurt Maeder (born 10 September 1952) is a Swiss equestrian. He competed in the individual jumping event at the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1952 births Category:Living people Category:Swiss male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Switzerland Category:Equestrians at the 1972 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
